      <title>New TDR designed Seefeel SOL.HZ album cover featuring bespoke ‘Sfl(4e)’ logo bui...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DWD1ztGjA5R/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/655208895_18571058389049614_3972878158464002454_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NjE2MTg0OTUyODMzODU5OQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjExNjh4MTU0NC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=zpg4sm2ryekQ7kNvwFma5mT&amp;_nc_oc=Adp1tnRpJDjJWP-olREgT8eIBDZbM5rB0l8wLN9fE-PkfcUxZP7DKimSZAYMjuUMOMc&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=Xs40q8znYgKltaWfm_Ok8g&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwHkzzPWu7AyXdDpgvZu4vuTafTsOQdSv1up2LmF64azg&amp;oe=69C9B84A" alt="Instagram billede fra @thedesignersrepublic" /></p><p><strong>@thedesignersrepublic</strong></p><p>New TDR designed Seefeel SOL.HZ album cover featuring bespoke ‘Sfl(4e)’ logo built from (and corroded by) letterforms improvised as part the 6x26 un-gridded modular alphabets forming the basis for the TDRRunes project (potentially infinite WIP) exploring the parameters of legibility abstracting understanding beyond knowledge. <br/>
<br/>
TDRRunes is ultimately a plan to create user editable typographic digital artefacts for end-use anywhere and anyhow… but right now we’re having a fine time road testing being the end-users ourselves. This spells how we see Seefeel feeling… new beginnings in every memory… supernova sunsets...<br/>
<br/>
TDRRunes began as a way of spelling numbers, evolving from the TDRBingo NFT project. It might end up being something very different… it always does.<br/>
<br/>
#seefeel #typography #graphicdesign #recordcovers #glitch</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/655208895_18571058389049614_3972878158464002454_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NjE2MTg0OTUyODMzODU5OQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjExNjh4MTU0NC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=zpg4sm2ryekQ7kNvwFma5mT&amp;_nc_oc=Adp1tnRpJDjJWP-olREgT8eIBDZbM5rB0l8wLN9fE-PkfcUxZP7DKimSZAYMjuUMOMc&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=Xs40q8znYgKltaWfm_Ok8g&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwHkzzPWu7AyXdDpgvZu4vuTafTsOQdSv1up2LmF64azg&amp;oe=69C9B84A" alt="Instagram billede fra @thedesignersrepublic" /></p><p><strong>@thedesignersrepublic</strong></p><p>New TDR designed Seefeel SOL.HZ album cover featuring bespoke ‘Sfl(4e)’ logo built from (and corroded by) letterforms improvised as part the 6x26 un-gridded modular alphabets forming the basis for the TDRRunes project (potentially infinite WIP) exploring the parameters of legibility abstracting understanding beyond knowledge. <br/>
<br/>
TDRRunes is ultimately a plan to create user editable typographic digital artefacts for end-use anywhere and anyhow… but right now we’re having a fine time road testing being the end-users ourselves. This spells how we see Seefeel feeling… new beginnings in every memory… supernova sunsets...<br/>
<br/>
TDRRunes began as a way of spelling numbers, evolving from the TDRBingo NFT project. It might end up being something very different… it always does.<br/>
<br/>
#seefeel #typography #graphicdesign #recordcovers #glitch</p>]]></content:encoded>
